title: CM- New, luxury 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom
posting_body: Welcome to 1836 Colby LLC, a newly constructed Wiseman community perfectly located just Off of Santa Monica Blvd in the heart of West LA.

This modern, luxury apartment building is comprised of 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom residences with open floor plans, designer fixtures, in-suite washers and dryers, walk-in closets, luxury appliances and more.
Moments away from great dining, easy freeway access, and beyond, and is the perfect lifestyle choice for those searching to be close to the coast.
Experience good living as Wiseman's friendly and professional leasing, management and maintenance teams cater to your needs.
